description: Don't take off for your next destination without the Men's FlyQ Vest. Its quick-drying and abrasion-resistant nylon fabric features a the rain- and stain-resistant Teflon™ Shield+ treatment so you keep moving day after day. Multiple exterior zippered hand and chest pockets and the interior 9-Pocket Travel System hold your glasses, passport, phone, and other essentials. An adjustable drawcord at the bottom hem offers a secure fit.
name: ExOfficio FlyQ Vest - Mens
